{"word":"ἠΰτε","slug":"ἠΰτε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n47655\" key=\"h)u/+te\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἠΰτε</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Particle, <sense id=\"n47655.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">as, like as</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠ. κούρη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:872\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.872</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἠ. νεβρός</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0199.tlg001:12:87\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.87</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; freq. in similes, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:359\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.359</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:87\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.87</biblScope></bibl>, etc.: after a <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Comp.\">Comp.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῷ δέ τ᾽ ἄνευθεν ἐόντι μελάντερον ἠ. πίσσα φαίνεται</foreign> [the cloud] appears to him while afar off very black, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">even as</tr_> pitch, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:277\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.277</biblScope></bibl>, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> Sch.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔχετο κλαίουσ᾽ ἀδινώτερον, ἠΰτε κούρη</foreign> with sobs coming quicker and quicker, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">like</tr_> a girl, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:269\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.269</biblScope> </bibl>; but it may <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">=</abbr> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">than</tr_> in these passages; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὖτε. </foreign>(<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἤ</foreign> + I.-<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> </bibl> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ute</tr_> (cf. Skt. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">uta</tr_>) 'also', 'even'.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}